{"type":"text","timestamp":1775848692640,"sessionID":"ses_28730ac95ffeAn455E0f48zV8R","part":{"id":"prt_d78d4707b001LgH9aTuSj4YiX1","messageID":"msg_d78d45585001hAh2jkycDD9ZN4","sessionID":"ses_28730ac95ffeAn455E0f48zV8R","type":"text","text":"I've successfully created the `delta-spec.md` file for **AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理** at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md`.\n\nThe specification includes **608 lines** covering:\n\n## Key Requirements with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios:\n\n1. **Sandbox Single Deletion Endpoint** - Delete by session ID, custom graceful timeout, 404/409 handling\n2. **Sandbox Force Delete Endpoint** - Bypass graceful shutdown, immediate termination\n3. **Sandbox Batch Deletion Endpoint** - Parallel deletion, partial failures, size limits\n4. **Graceful Shutdown Flow** - Configurable timeout, graceful vs force handling\n5. **Resource Cleanup** - K8s resources, owner references, retry logic\n6. **Lifecycle State Management** - State tracking, history, filtering\n7. **Idle Detection Background Worker** - Auto-delete idle sandboxes, grace periods\n8. **Orphan Cleanup Background Worker** - Detect orphan CRs and zombie Store entries\n9. **Idempotency and Concurrency** - Duplicate requests, concurrent batch deletes\n10. **Error Handling** - HTTP status mapping, validation errors\n11. **Authentication Integration** - RBAC, per-user K8s clients\n12. **Configuration** - Environment variable support\n\n## File Structure:\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle/handler/` - HTTP handlers\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle/manager/` - Lifecycle orchestration\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle/detector/` - Background workers\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle/types/` - Data types\n\n## API Endpoints:\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| DELETE | `/v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` | Delete AgentRuntime sandbox |\n| DELETE | `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` | Delete CodeInterpreter sandbox |\n| DELETE | `/v1/sandboxes` | Batch delete |\n| POST | `/v1/sandboxes/:sessionId/terminate` | Force terminate |\n| GET | `/v1/sandboxes/:sessionId/lifecycle` | Get lifecycle state |","time":{"start":1775848692637,"end":1775848692637}}}
